Scope for the Current Phase

The current phase focuses on three key value streams: BFF (Business Finance Function), Financial Controls, and Treasury and Data. While many of the observations and proposed guidelines identified during this phase are expected to have broader applicability across other functions, the emphasis remains on these targeted areas. A more detailed analysis of upstream and downstream systems is planned for the subsequent phase of the discussions, enabling a comprehensive understanding of dependencies and integration points.

